{
  "stem": "5275.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember one incident in which I bought a goose in the German part, and put it on my wagon, and covered it with a thing, and I was about to leave when the Germans passed by and the goose started [LAUGHS] making noise.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So of course, they discovered me, but all I had to do is to give them the goose, and they left, and I came back to the school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It wasn't the worst of times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was scary time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The German-- the Russian front came and the artillery barrage started.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were sitting in the kitchen of the director's house, and I was making butter-- you know, the thing that you pull up and down, up and down.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was doing that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one of the shells-- oh, by the way, we have learned very quickly which were the German shells and which were the Russian shells, because when the Russians were shooting, there was this explosion, the noise, and then you could hear this wind kind of swish sound.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When the Germans were shooting, you could hear the swish sound first and then was the explosion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So we learned very quickly which one is dangerous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But anyhow, one of the shells exploded right outside the kitchen with a horrendous thing, and I was doing this butter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everybody in the kitchen went panicky, went under the table.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was sitting there making the butter, and I wouldn't stop, because I had to make the butter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this became so proverbial that every time something happened in the future, they were referring to me making this butter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, this follow me even here, because some friends learned about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
